data.description: This is such an adorable well-maintained home you will fall in love as soon as you reach the curb. Detached two-car garage/workshop in the back along with a shed. Large fenced back yard with lush, fragrant landscaping featuring gardenia, jasmine, plumeria, star fruit and more. Room for the boat, trailer, RV and pool! Interior was newly remodeled including new cabinets, quartz countertops, water heater and more. Newer AC and hurricane windows. Low expenses through energy-efficient block construction and county water with septic. Must see to appreciate the care the homeowners have put into this home.
